Others: Nic Claxton scored 10 points on 5 of 8 shooting, grabbed 8 rebounds, handed out 3 assists, notched 2 steals, and blocked a shot in a season-high 26:38 in his first start of the season.
Dorian Finney-Smith had 17 points (6 of 10 and a Nets career-high-tying 5 of 8 from deep) with 6 boards in 28 minutes.
Noah Clowney missed Monday's game with a sore hip, but he's hopeful of playing their next game in Boston.
